I want to show some Covid-19 information, and we can look wheter the Covid-19 is still very serious in Honduras. Then, we also will find some interest information

Table 1: the summary of the Covid-19 in Honduras
confirmed deaths recivered average_new_cases
340559 8960 102384 579.182

This is the data summary for the Honduras data. From the table, we can see the total confirmed, total deaths, total recovered and the average increase of the new cases. We know the population of the Honduras is \(9904607\) from the Wikipedia. The number of total confirmed case is 3.4201963% of the total population. The number of the total deaths is 0.0893524% of the total population. Now, more than $2.27523*10^{5} $ people are strugle with the Covid-19. Then, now the number of case increase \(577\) every day on average

This is historical table, it is a interactive table, we can play with it, and see all historicial data since 2020 Jan.

This is time series plot. it shows that the the number of confirmed case increase very quick. Compared with confirmed case, the number of deaths shows a slowing increase. Finally, this is a interactive graph, we can play with it.

Conclusion

I have shown some table and graph, it looks like that the the confirmed case may continue to increase. it may has a long impact in Honduras.
